<p>Lauren's sultry snap comes as she revealed in this week's New! magazine that she hasn't spoke to her family or parents since finding fame. </p>

<p>She told the publication: 'No, I don't talk to any of them and they don't talk to me. They're good people, I'm not going to s**g them off. I just can't have that in my life.</p>

