<p>Lauren's mother Cheryl 'rejected' her as a child and she lived with her father at just four-years-old, who started his 'own life'.  </p>

<p>She told New! magazine: 'No, I don't talk to any of them and they don't talk to me. They're good people, I'm not going to s**g them off. I just can't have that in my life.'  </p>

